[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "この島に着いてから、私たちはホルハーツの\n有力者の方々に物資の協力をお願いしに行ったんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でも、異国の人間がこの島と深く関わるなら、\n大きな愛を見せてほしいって言われちゃって……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ロマンさんが王国名物を贈呈したらしいんだけど、\nそういう問題じゃないって一喝されちゃったみたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "結局、愛を認めてもらうには、もうすぐ開催される\n「愛のレース」で優勝するしかないみたいなんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ここまで独自の価値観の島だとは思わなかったなぁ。\n文化の違いってすごいよね……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ふふ、なかなか面白い島じゃない。\n「愛のレース」って、どんな内容なの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それが……ホルハーツ鳥っていう、\nこの島固有の鳥のメスを探し出すレースみたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ホルハーツ鳥は、諸島で絶滅危惧種に\n指定されてる鳥なんすよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "今はオスの個体しか保護されていないみたいで。\nでも最近、島の湿地でメスの目撃情報があったんだって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そのメスを保護できれば、ホルハーツ鳥の繁殖を\n手助けできて、島の人たちも大喜びってわけ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "だから報奨金を出して、\nレース形式で盛り上げてるんすよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "なるほどな。ホルハーツ鳥の愛を手助けすることが\n大きな愛を見せることに繋がるってわけか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "優勝しないと協力してもらえないんでしょ？　\nだったら、参加しない理由はないわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "はい！　フロッケも頑張ります。\nみんなで力を合わせれば、きっと見つけられますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "天使ちゃん、ケガだけはすんなよ。\n俺も全力でやるからな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それじゃ、運営本部に向かいましょ。\n受付で詳しい取り決めも聞けるはずよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "案内はアタシに任せて！\n受付の場所はもうバッチリ把握してるから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "みんなで無事に参加できますように……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "みんな、ありがとう。\nよろしくお願いします！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "愛の島で一番大きな愛ってやつを見せてやるわよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]